node.text:
Who’s coming with us to the Maldives?! 💦🌊🏝 Nothing but white sand, turquoise water and blue sky is waiting for you...

An island country in the Indian Ocean southwest of Sri Lanka, consisting of about 20 atolls made up of more than 2,000 coral islands.

📽 @mvandersluis
📍Maldives
🎶 Landon Austin•Girls Like You
